{
  "stem": "5388.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So maybe it was kind of-- you would have to bring almost in strangers or-- from another city or town.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm looking for a towel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Here I had it, and I don't know where I put it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Oh, never mind.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And then, as the-- the-- the war came closer, and the summer of '39 and so on, do you remember anything about the Russian-German pact, the Molotov-Ribbentrop pact?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that's already when the war started.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know about that, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I learned it later on in history.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But at that time, I did not know about the Ribbentrop-Molotov pact of August 23, I think it was, 1939, or 22.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And no, I knew nothing about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then suddenly, the war was started, and I was in Suwalki.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Our-- our relatives, I was sick with the mumps or measles or something, a child disease.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and I remember Suwalki was bombed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Suwalki used to have those military barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was not too far from the border, that under the Russians, it was already a military out-- it also had a big military post.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because it was also on the border with Germany. 1914, I'm talking about.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the same place remained on the border between Poland and Germany after the First World War.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was sent there away from the border.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I suppose.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Big deal, it was only 10 kilometers, 15 kilometers from it, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was with Brenner, B-R-E-N-N-E-R.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Poland, we spelled it, I think, with one N.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But anyhow, that's [HEBREW]-- my mother's sister, she was married to Alter Brenner.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were in Suwalki.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
